          New Conference
        </button>
      </div>

      <div className="flex-1 overflow-y-auto pr-2 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 pb-6 scrollbar-thin scrollbar-thumb-slate-700">
